{"talk":{"id":68725,"name":"Sophie Rose: How COVID-19 human challenge trials work -- and why I volunteered","description":"In April 2020, epidemiologist-in-training Sophie Rose volunteered to be infected with the virus that causes COVID-19. As a young, healthy adult, she's offering to take part in a human challenge trial, a study where participants are intentionally exposed to SARS-CoV-2 to test vaccines and gather critical data. Explaining how challenge trials could speed up the development of effective vaccines, Rose shares why volunteering was the right decision for her.","slug":"sophie_rose_how_covid_19_human_challenge_trials_work_and_why_i_volunteered","recorded_at":"2020-11-12 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-11-20 20:47:24","updated_at":"2021-10-22 20:59:42","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":659,"name":"TEDWomen 2020"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7bb2401ceeeccf19536cb70c5174f170f73d6828_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7bb2401ceeeccf19536cb70c5174f170f73d6828_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7bb2401ceeeccf19536cb70c5174f170f73d6828_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7bb2401ceeeccf19536cb70c5174f170f73d6828_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/09a882c5e9e66bf21893bdf43246cc01638f04fe_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/SophieRose_2020W-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":3276987,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/SophieRose_2020W-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":8997872,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/SophieRose_2020W-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":159